{"tid":233334,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)懲罰者 怒海救援 2019獵血都市","createTime":"2017-05-07T13:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T19:29:31.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a54904c303f75c226ff0382b4541e1eb7b40d39b","tid":233334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9814a829\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ef310443\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=820a1fde\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://b0.rimg.tw/samuel1711/77d7e8ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fb0.rimg.tw%2Fsamuel1711%2F77d7e8ba.jpg&h=7caa812b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2e/The_Finest_Hours_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F2e%2FThe_Finest_Hours_Poster.jpg&h=6bbd02a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b4/Daybreakers_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb4%2FDaybreakers_ver2.jpg&h=47c0778f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特（托馬斯&middot;簡Thomas Jane 飾）的生命中，絕大部分時間都在於死神賽跑。早年在海軍陸戰隊服役，退役後又進入FBI。在槍砲火光中生活了多年之後，弗蘭克不願再整日收到死亡的威脅，家人整日為他擔驚受怕。所以，他決定提前退休與妻兒享受平靜的生活。可是，在最後的一次任務中，卻因意外使一名無辜青年死亡。而這名青年的父親卻是坦帕市的大富商霍華德&middot;桑特（約翰&middot;特拉沃塔John Travolta 飾）。為了給兒子報仇..<br />\n<br />\n2.改編自真實災難事件，一場規模空前的風暴在美國東北角掀起駭人狂風和滔天巨浪，兩艘大型油輪就在狂風暴雨中撞裂成兩半。一組海岸防衛隊冒著生命危險，在零下低溫和70英尺的巨浪威脅下，靠著單薄的救生艇，要與時間和天氣競賽，搶救岌岌可危的油輪組員性命..<br />\n<br />\n3.電影情節設置在未來的2019年，世界成了吸血鬼的天下，由於人類越來越少，吸血鬼急需研究出血液的替代品，血液專家愛德華&middot;道爾頓（伊森&middot;霍克飾）從事這項工作，其老闆查爾斯&middot;布羅姆利（薩姆&middot;尼爾飾）是一位野心家，他希望通過壟斷新的替代品獲得巨額利潤。愛德華&middot;道爾頓在一次意外結識了人類奧德麗&middot;班尼特（克勞迪婭&middot;卡梵飾），通過她認識了在一次意外中由吸血鬼奇蹟般變成人類的「艾維斯」（威廉&middot;達佛飾），在三人的共同努力下，找到了由吸血鬼變成人類的方法..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49485b3a795d62fa245d1e014783b42f13b399d","tid":233334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cde701d1ce08cc8d342935d517837362ea04bd","tid":233334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723cb34787cc17cd28f567430f0cb1cd3b9c769b","tid":233334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ccde2848178a3f80369ab75ee4081f7dde7992","tid":233334,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited